title: Computerized Associate Practice Test & Study Guide
description: Software program featuring 350 sample questions for the Associate CET exam. May also be used for ESA Program study. Each problem has a short explanation of how the problem is solved. The student can randomly select 75 problems for a practice test, or review difficult sections repeatedly. Compatible with Windows 95/98/NT/XP/Vista. Windows 95/98/NT version requires monitor resolution of 800x600, 256 colors, 2.4 MB of disk space, and CD-ROM drive. Please note that this CD does not have audio.
